  <!--
    Comprehensive Test Data for TIGERReview JOSM Plugin
    ===================================================

    This file tests scenarios NOT covered by tiger-review-test.osm and
    test-data-surface-validation.osm.  It focuses on:

      A. Invalid / edge-case tiger:reviewed values
      B. Residual tiger:* tag cleanup
      C. Alignment-reviewed roads (aerial / position / alignment)
      D. Connected-road corroboration trust rules
      E. Highway type filtering (included and excluded)
      F. Bot exclusion for all built-in bots
      G. Alignment evidence bucket boundaries
      H. Name / tag edge cases
      I. Surface confidence tiers and non-vehicular filtering
      J. Address check edge cases
      K. Fully-verified decision matrix combinations
      L. Two-node minimal ways

    Load in JOSM and run the validator to test.

    TESTING NOTE: Nodes can use these tags:
    - __TEST_VERSION : Override node version
    - __TEST_USER   : Override last editor username
  -->


